high_descs: walk over to the kitchen stove
pick up the tea kettle off of the kitchen stove
walk over to the black dining table
place the tea kettle on top of the black dining table
turn around and walk over to the far end kitchen counter
pick up the tea kettle off of the kitchen counter
walk back over to the black dining room table
place the tea kettle on the black table behind the other tea kettle
anns.task_desc: place two tea kettles on the black dining room table

high_descs: Turn left, go to the oven.
Take the kettle from the front left burner of the stove top.
Turn left go to between the round table and the trash can, then face the round table.
Put the kettle above the bowl and to the left of the plant on the round table.
Turn left, go in front of the dishwasher on the right of the sink.
Take the kettle to the right of the coffee maker on the counter.
Turn left go to between the round table and the trash can, then face the round table.
Put the kettle above the other kettle near the edge of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put two kettles on a round table.

high_descs: Turn left and go towards the stove.
Pick up the kettle from the stove top.
Turn left and go forward, turn left again so you are facing the black table.
Put the kettle pot on the table.
Turn around and go right back towards the stove but go past the stove.
Turn left at the dishwasher and coffee maker, facing it.
Turn back around and go left towards the black table.
Put another kettle pot on the table next to the other.
anns.task_desc: Moving kettle pots to the table.
